{"tid":2183582,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"關於《動物農莊》中豬所說的平等 ，我哋拍咗條片，歡迎各位黎睇吓。","createTime":"2020-09-01T04:27:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-01T07:41:32.000Z","uid":32126,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"708a28f209f52d7856b7253f1dbabc70d14930a6","tid":2183582,"uid":32126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T04:27:25.000Z","msg":"事源前排拍片搵素材先見到《動物農莊》。<br />\n<br />\n睇完之後發現,咁多年來共產主義嘅歷史都冇變過。<br />\n<br />\n如果大家無睇過動物農莊,可以睇一睇我哋拍嘅尼條片。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/WVL9AVJKbRw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FWVL9AVJKbRw&d=X54jjuw0UQFZuhWzkrVO7m58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=f4c0fb55\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/WVL9AVJKbRw</a><br />\n<br />\n因為細個好鍾意當年今日尼種題材嘅節目，<br />\n<br />\n所以就自己都拍翻套類似嘅冷知識影片。<br />\n<br />\n做到上個星期講到《動物農莊》，<br />\n<br />\n再睇翻今日我哋所面對嘅一切，<br />\n<br />\n個故事當年係諷刺蘇聯，<br />\n<br />\n但到今日都係一樣，我哋嘅歷史好似不斷重複咁。<br />\n<br />\n楊潤雄話香港從來都無三權分立⋯<br />\n<br />\n一切嘅內容同動物農莊一模一樣。<br />\n<br />\n「All animals are equal but some animals are more equal than others.」<br />\n<br />\n這，就是豬群們的平等。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港人，加油！"},{"pid":"0c7b3fcb1e36bdb05f566bdf03c95275e0687fd7","tid":2183582,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T04:29:34.000Z","msg":"支持左先"},{"pid":"2c295bba8d974493cac4ff71b3063aa51b4bc447","tid":2183582,"uid":32126,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T04:30:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YFeM86u.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYFeM86u.png&h=d3846dfd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"59971cb8a1d0ce6e8728f66be1a71a25df7448aa","tid":2183582,"uid":32126,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T04:34:46.000Z","msg":"動物農莊當初提出咗動物七戒如下：<br />\n<br />\n凡兩條腿走路的，都是敵人；<br />\n<br />\n凡四條腿走路的，或有翅膀的，都是朋友； <br />\n<br />\n凡動物不可穿衣；<br />\n<br />\n凡動物不可睡在床上； <br />\n<br />\n凡動物不可飲酒； <br />\n<br />\n動物不可殺害動物；  <br />\n<br />\n所有動物一律平等。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最終都不過係一次又一次被當權者所打破違背。<br />\n<br />\n多麼諷刺⋯"},{"pid":"ef5181ef8ff4279bea7f786efbf929fb63c091e3","tid":2183582,"uid":48719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T04:40:58.000Z","msg":"G持"},{"pid":"615efcad6ab812eedd3205109212078769040cf2","tid":2183582,"uid":32126,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T04:45:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2caP6Ya.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2caP6Ya.jpg&h=c02bda65&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a751510c2680df7033d1bb3b3c7bab4277bf7f91","tid":2183582,"uid":32126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T04:49:50.000Z","msg":"喬治&middot;奧威爾於1943年11月至1944年2月間創作本書，<br />\n<br />\n當時英國同蘇聯是戰時盟友，<br />\n<br />\n而英國的百姓和知識分子都對斯大林評價很高，這一現象讓奧威爾十分厭惡。<br />\n<br />\n本書的手稿，起初被許多英美出版商拒絕出版。<br />\n<br />\n但本書問世以後獲得了巨大的成功，其部分原因是由於原<br />\n<br />\n來同英國是戰時盟友的蘇聯與西方世界開始了冷戰。<br />\n<br />\n《時代雜誌》將《動物莊園》評選為1923-2005年100佳<br />\n<br />\n英文小說；它亦在20世紀百大英文小說中排第31位。<br />\n<br />\n它在1996年贏得追頒雨果獎，此外也包括在西方世界偉大<br />\n著作名單之上。"},{"pid":"310c780a9e969f6ece246f45d5f3d57bcbbfe97c","tid":2183582,"uid":182624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T04:55:30.000Z","msg":"值得一睇"},{"pid":"e0aafb78962feb36b509f9d82ac6ad05d3b4aa9e","tid":2183582,"uid":182624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T04:55:41.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"f33f7c527641d4e8146291fe2656826c67deab09","tid":2183582,"uid":142888,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T05:02:12.000Z","msg":"我記得仲有一個情節係當Sonwball同拿破崙進行辯論或當有其他動物反對拿破崙嗰陣，啲羊就叫four legs good; two legs bad. 打擾佢哋，支持拿破崙<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n即使諗起啲藍絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b20a5bf9be93065385d5b0f6acd307adce95fbd","tid":2183582,"uid":32126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f33f7c527641d4e8146291fe2656826c67deab09","tid":2183582,"u