 />\n另有一番風味<br />\n<br />\nRules每日改緊<br />\n郁啲唔岩就話人係鬼<br />\n山羊係咁和應<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T05:12:14.000Z","msg":"改規則就好似宜家嘅香港咁<br />\n<br />\n溫水煮蛙<br />\n<br />\n山羊就係藍絲<br />\n<br />\n當權者一定唔會錯"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T05:16:18.000Z","msg":"山羊係咪無論邊個當權<br />\n都係支持當權者？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T05:17:30.000Z","msg":"牆頭草 可以咁樣認為<br />\n<br />\n對佢哋而言 最緊要係唔好影響到佢哋"},{"pid":"b8c612d4b5ca7f8be95ef5a7df125b1ed98bf420","tid":2183582,"uid":32126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7ee61dc81ebb72f63820ab9cf615bf47caee0522","tid":2183582,"uid":78307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T05:16:10.000Z","msg":"Animal farm 咁耐之前嘅書都同現令一模一樣 歷史果然唔會導人向善<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zQAsTN2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzQAsTN2.jpg&h=14bb5638&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T05:20:21.000Z","msg":"突然發現<br />\n經濟同歷史都一樣 都係不斷循環<br />\n但總有人永遠唔會從中吸取教訓<br />\n永遠行翻上條舊路"},{"pid":"639c995c5e550bbaf9bc234cfbe95b93ed6f5819","tid":2183582,"uid":34804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ec8d6570ddf0c7479aef4b46516f998a8faf253","tid":2183582,"uid":32126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"254f07a83d71301925c65a3921f7d23c88b28c90","tid":2183582,"uid":71836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5189ae7111159877d6d05bf1d08cd9950f3f353","tid":2183582,"uid":32126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T05:12:14.000Z","msg":"改規則就好似宜家嘅香港咁<br />\n<br />\n溫水煮蛙<br />\n<br />\n山羊就係藍絲<br />\n<br />\n當權者一定唔會錯"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T05:16:18.000Z","msg":"山羊係咪無論邊個當權<br />\n都係支持當權者？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T05:17:30.000Z","msg":"牆頭草 可以咁樣認為<br />\n<br />\n對佢哋而言 最緊要係唔好影響到佢哋"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T05: